title: ArtyTorrent Pack 66-Funky Breaks 120-129bpm-WAV samples
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 66-Funky Breaks 120-129bpm-WAV samples
-------------------------------------------------------

Same tempo range as the previous pack, but this time the breaks have more of an organic live feel. Includes several loops with a 2-step feel for RnB, speed garage, bassline house or whatever they call it these days.
The tempo ranges from 120-129 bpm, so general house fans should also find this pack useful. 

Torrent contains 6 RAR files with 113 loops
-------------------------------------------
2-Step Garage RnB 120-129 (23 loops)
Acid Fanatic Funky Breaks 120 (8 loops)
Breakbeat 124 (8 loops)
DDT Breakz 120-129 (48 loops)
Misc Funky Breaks 120-129 (22 loops)
Punked Up 125 (3 loops)

Samples are from a variety of sources too numerous to mentionm but have all been normalized and acidized as 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz.

Comments/thanks/requests are welcome.

--
Arty - "Funk Soul Brother"
16th February 2008.
